description: [``botocore``] AWS IAM Access Analyzer policy validation introduces new checks for role trust policies. As customers author a policy, IAM Access Analyzer policy validation evaluates the policy for any issues to make it easier for customers to author secure policies.
[``botocore``] Adding an imdsSupport attribute to EC2 AMIs
[``botocore``] Adds support for V3_5C. This is a refreshed AWS Snowball Edge Compute Optimized device type with 28TB SSD, 104 vCPU and 416GB memory (customer usable).
